0:05:24.26,000 --> 0:05:26,000
This number is small.

133
0:05:26.26,000 --> 0:05:28,000
Expressed in the relevant unit,

134
0:05:28.26,000 --> 0:05:3,000
it is spectacularly small.

135
0:05:30.26,000 --> 0:05:33,000
And the mystery is to explain this peculiar number.

136
0:05:33.26,000 --> 0:05:35,000
We want this number

137
0:05:35.26,000 --> 0:05:37,000
to emerge from the laws of physics,

138
0:05:37.26,000 --> 0:05:4,000
