0:05:49.26,000 --> 0:05:52,000
a technical detail of interest to experts,

144
0:05:52.26,000 --> 0:05:54,000
but of no relevance to anybody else.

145
0:05:54.26,000 --> 0:05:57,000
Well it surely is a technical detail,

146
0:05:57.26,000 --> 0:05:59,000
