0:06:12.26,000 --> 0:06:15,000
an idea that naturally emerges from string theory,

153
0:06:15.26,000 --> 0:06:18,000
which takes me to part two: string theory.

154
0:06:18.26,000 --> 0:06:22,000
So hold the mystery of the dark energy

155
0:06:22.26,000 --> 0:06:24,000
in the back of your mind

156
0:06:24.26,000 --> 0:06:26,000
as I now go on to tell you

157
0:06:26.26,000 --> 0:06:29,000
three key things about string theory.

158
0:06:29.26,000 --> 0:06:31,000
First off, what is it?

