0:17:27.26,000 --> 0:17:29,000
And if our universe got hit by another,

419
0:17:29.26,000 --> 0:17:31,000
that collision

420
0:17:31.26,000 --> 0:17:33,000
would generate an additional subtle pattern

421
0:17:33.26,000 --> 0:17:35,000
of temperature variations across space

422
0:17:35.26,000 --> 0:17:37,000
that we might one day

423
0:17:37.26,000 --> 0:17:39,000
be able to detect.

