0:17:39.26,000 --> 0:17:42,000
And so exotic as this picture is,

425
0:17:42.26,000 --> 0:17:44,000
it may one day be grounded

426
0:17:44.26,000 --> 0:17:46,000
in observations,

427
0:17:46.26,000 --> 0:17:49,000
establishing the existence of other universes.

428
0:17:49.26,000 --> 0:17:51,000
I'll conclude

429
0:17:51.26,000 --> 0:17:54,000
with a striking implication

430
0:17:54.26,000 --> 0:17:56,000
of all these ideas

431
0:17:56.26,000 --> 0:17:58,000
for the very far future.

432
0:17:58.26,000 --> 0:18:,000
You see, we learned

433
0:18:00.26,000 --> 0:18:02,000
that our universe is not static,

